{"tid":2042573,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"5.27濫捕 200人扣留兩日始保釋","createTime":"2020-05-30T01:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T01:51:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b86a71ea18ef0e471d8b2552b42f06a54607e712","tid":2042573,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:51:28.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200530/KIFVLA6GP6DBFVNKLQK3YFGMMI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200530%2FKIFVLA6GP6DBFVNKLQK3YFGMMI%2F&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=c5db1d10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200530%2FKIFVLA6GP6DBFVNKLQK3YFGMMI%2F&h=9de22074\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200530/KIFVLA6GP6DBFVNKLQK3YFGMMI/</a><br />\n<br />\n5.27濫捕 200人扣留兩日始保釋<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本周三高中復課日警方在全港無差別濫捕396人，包括180名學生，當中80名未成年人士前日已獲釋，其餘200多人在扣留近40小時後。。。。。。。。。。。。口供紙及擔保書上所列的涉嫌罪名有出入，對警方處理感到奇怪。<br />\n<br />\n不少獲釋人士均指，當時只是在銅鑼灣路過、約朋友午膳、或前往購物途中便遭警方無理拘捕。林小姐憶述事發時與朋友在利舞臺附近購物後離開，與朋友沿行人路前行，卻遭大批警員呼喝驅趕「上返行人路」及舉起黃旗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://thumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub/Q0K6xqfi0K_MFbQNae3c28XxIwI=/arc-photo-appledaily/ap-ne-1-prod/public/GM2ZCGOK5IEKTPP6OSYJUYPWZM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub%2FQ0K6xqfi0K_MFbQNae3c28XxIwI%3D%2Farc-photo-appledaily%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FGM2ZCGOK5IEKTPP6OSYJUYPWZM.gif&h=1772d60a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批被捕者家屬昨凌晨於北角警署外通宵等候。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n購物市民被捕 轟警不聽解釋<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：國防七校 四間被美禁購零件<br />\n<br />\n林小姐過馬路途中。。。。。。。。。。。。林小姐不忿稱：「我手上仲有購物單據，但警員唔聽解釋！」她指當日下午約2時40分被捕，兩個多小時後已錄畢口供及打指模，但竟要呆坐36小時至昨凌晨才獲保釋。<br />\n<br />\n中六生關同學途經灣仔軒尼詩道時被防暴警員截停分成男女兩行，警員釋放數人後拘捕其他人，並指警員粗言穢語喊打喊殺，在警署內又拍枱，但「最奇怪錄口供時話涉嫌參與一個未經批准集結，口供紙係咁寫，但保釋紙卻寫涉嫌參與非法集結，前後不符」。<br />\n<br />\n今次大濫捕中警方在全港拘捕396人（12至70歲）。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李家傑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://thumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub/ZZ2mV-HB7lRGQxFh6Z3dvimA63g=/arc-photo-appledaily/ap-ne-1-prod/public/KMFYD6WUHV6BHNQPZKXK6EQGC4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub%2FZZ2mV-HB7lRGQxFh6Z3dvimA63g%3D%2Farc-photo-appledaily%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FKMFYD6WUHV6BHNQPZKXK6EQGC4.gif&h=a4a0ca5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有獲釋者質疑警方保釋紙所寫控罪與口供紙不符。"}]}